# Steps to install SASS

1. (Optional) Install Node version 20.16 on Ubuntu using nvm:
   curl -o- https://raw.githubusercontent.com/nvm-sh/nvm/v0.39.7/install.sh | bash
   exit
   Reopen terminal and run:
   nvm install 20.16

2. Install SASS globally (or locally) with npm:
   npm install sass -v 3.7.4

3. Verify installation:
   sass --version

